snippet.title: Dwarven Realms - Official Announcement Trailer | OTK Games Expo 2024
snippet.description:
Dwarven Realms is a hack-and-slash action RPG developed by Crater Studios. Players will utilize epic powers, powerful builds, and endless permutations to unleash mayhem on hordes of enemies. Dwarven Realms is available now in Steam Early Access for PC with Season 1 launching in Summer 2024.

#Gaming #Games #GameTrailers
